# IGNORED: DEPLOYMENT CONFIG
# ============================================
# Vercel deployment configuration folder - not used in Docker builds
.vercel

# ============================================
# IGNORED: LOG FILES
# ============================================
# Application logs - excluded to keep image clean
*.log